The paper deals with semantic analysis and information retrieval, which are key topics in the field of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The use of Wikipedia categories and the evaluation on a text classification task suggest that the paper also belongs to the sub-category of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL). The use of tf-idf and machine learning techniques for semantic analysis and classification suggest that the paper could also belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Deep Learning (cs.DL).
